sequenceDiagram
    actor Caller
    participant Tw as Twilio Voice (ASR+TTS)
    participant App as Sales Agent (WS service)
    participant Claude as Claude (brain)
    participant Inv as Inventory DB (read)
    participant Leads as Leads DB (write)

    Caller->>Tw: Dials (876) 499-0815
    Tw->>App: POST /voice
    App-->>Tw: TwiML <Connect><ConversationRelay wss://…>
    Tw-->>Caller: Speaks welcome greeting (ElevenLabs)
    Tw->>App: WS open + setup/connected (callSid, from)

    loop Each caller turn
        Caller->>Tw: Speaks
        Tw->>App: prompt {voicePrompt: transcript}
        App->>Claude: messages.stream (system + history + tools)
        Claude-->>App: text tokens
        App-->>Tw: text {token, last:false} (streamed)
        opt Claude calls a tool
            Claude-->>App: tool_use (check_availability / capture_lead / …)
            App->>Inv: soft availability lookup
            Inv-->>App: per-branch stock
            App->>Leads: insert lead (scored)
            App->>Claude: tool_result
            Claude-->>App: follow-up text
            App-->>Tw: text {token, last:false}
        end
        App-->>Tw: text {token:"", last:true}
        Tw-->>Caller: Speaks reply
    end

    Caller->>Tw: Hangs up
    Tw->>App: WS close
    App->>Leads: insert call_log (transcript, duration)
